"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/890111","Cabinet Office","false","2018-04-26","<p>As stated in para 6.4 of the Strategic Supplier Risk Management policy (<a href="https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/government/uploads/system/uploads/attachment_data/file/80222/20121108_Strategic_Supplier_Risk_Management_Policy.pdf" target="_blank">https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/government/uploads/system/uploads/attachment_data/file/80222/20121108_Strategic_Supplier_Risk_Management_Policy.pdf</a> Cabinet Office does not publish supplier ratings.</p>","Hertsmere","Oliver Dowden",,"2018-04-26T11:42:28.773Z","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/890111/answer","Biography information for Oliver Dowden","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/890111/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/890111/answer",,,,,"53","Cabinet Office","Cabinet Office","2018-04-23","G4S","1","House of Commons","To ask the Minister for the Cabinet Office, whether his Department has designated G4S as a high risk strategic supplier.","false","Biography information for Paul Blomfield","Sheffield Central","Paul Blomfield","137161"
